   <div id="Safety">
    <h2>Safety</h2>
    <p>South Korea has the reputation of being a very safe country and it was my experience as well. I felt very comfortable and safe everywhere I went. Travelling to Korea as a solo female is generally not issue however you should still follow some basic safety rules: </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Do not give the address of your hotel to a stranger </li>
      <li>Steer clear of drugs</li>
      <li>Write down emergency info and keep it in your wallet</li>
      <li>Lock up your valuable items </li>
   </ul>

